<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="src/output.css" />
    <title>PageWhisper</title>
  </head>
  <body class="text-white bg-[url('/images/background.png')] bg-cover">
    <div class="cotainer m-2 flex">
      <div class="logo w-20 h-12">
        <div class="book-animation perspective-distant">
          <article
            class="... transform-3d rotate-x-51 rotate-z-43 shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:rotate-x-49 hover:rotate-z-38 hover:shadow-2xl"
          >
            <img
              class="mx-16 my-4"
              src="images/book-svgrepo-com.svg"
              width="80%"
              height="20%"
              alt="website logo"
            />
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="search w-[100%] items-center justify-center">
        <form
          class="w-[100%] my-2 py-4 flex justify-center"
          action="/search"
          method="post"
        >
          <input
            class="bg-gray-600 w-[80%] p-3 rounded-xl focus:outline-none placeholder-[#fff] text-center text-white shadow-[0px_12px_6px_rgba(255,255,255,0.6)]"
            type="text"
            name="search"
            placeholder="Search your notes hereðŸ“’"
            id="search"
          />
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="title h-[25vh] flex justify-center items-center font-serif text-5xl"
    >
      <style>
        /* Custom keyframes for typing effect */
        @keyframes typing {
          from {
            width: 0;
          }
          to {
            width: 55%;
          }
        }

        /* Applying animation */
        .typing {
          overflow: hidden; /* Prevents text from overflowing */
          white-space: nowrap; /* Keeps the text in a single line */
          width: 0; /* Initial width for animation */
          animation: typing 3s forwards;
          animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
        }
      </style>

      <h1 class="typing">PageWhisper: Your Notes, Your Stories</h1>
    </div>
    <div
      class="quote h-[5vh] flex justify-center items-center font-serif text-2xl"
    >
      <div class="book-animation perspective-distant">
        <article
          class="... transform-3d rotate-x-51 rotate-z-43 shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:rotate-x-49 hover:rotate-z-38 hover:shadow-2xl flex justify-center gap-2"
        >
          <img
            src="images/invert-start.svg"
            class="brightness-0 invert"
            width="15rem"
            height="15rem"
            alt="start"
          />
          <h2>Demo Quote for you haha</h2>
          <img
            src="images/invert-end.svg"
            class="brightness-0 invert"
            width="15rem"
            height="15rem"
            alt="end"
          />
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="add m-2 p-12 flex justify-center items-center">
      <a href="/add"><button
        class="bg-black p-4 rounded-xl focus:outline-none hover:ring-2 hover:ring-white text-white shadow-[0px_12px_6px_rgba(255,255,255,0.6)]"
      >
        Add a new note
      </button></a>
    </div>
    <section class="book list flex flex-col gap-2">
      <!-- ejs code -->
      <div class="book-item perspective-distant">
        <article
          class="... transform-3d rotate-x-51 rotate-z-43 shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:rotate-x-49 hover:rotate-z-38 hover:shadow-2xl"
        >
          <div class="book-item-container flex justify-center items-center">
            <div class="title font-serif text-2xl w-[30%] text-center m-2">
              Demo title
            </div>
            <div class="note w-[70%] m-4">
              Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. At
              voluptate exercitationem enim praesentium dignissimos dolorem Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Delectus, enim porro. Eveniet porro dolorum repudiandae totam distinctio quibusdam iure laudantium suscipit, maxime recusandae. Libero, cumque unde! Exercitationem, nam nisi quibusdam expedita, perferendis dolores obcaecati delectus debitis, error ad tenetur quae accusantium. Nemo!
          </div>
        
      </div>

      <div class="change flex justify-end my-4 mx-20 gap-8">
        <button
        class="bg-green-500 w-20 p-2 rounded-xl focus:outline-none hover:ring-2 hover:ring-white text-white"
        >
        Edit</button>
        <button
          class="bg-red-600 w-20 p-2 rounded-xl focus:outline-none hover:ring-2 hover:ring-white text-white"
          >
          Delete</button>
      </div>
    </article>
    </section>

